286
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:49,080
Anyway, Kevin Gable --
CEO and founder.

287
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:53,460
Wow! Honey,
look at all these people!

288
00:10:53,460 --> 00:10:56,040
It's working.

