want to ride with it.

298
00:11:08,420 --> 00:11:10,080
Okay, you're right,
you're right.

299
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:12,790
So, what's a girl got to do
to get some pho around here?

300
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,420
Oh, well, for <i>you...</i>

301
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,420
Yeah?

302
00:11:14,420 --> 00:11:15,920
