Chicken or beef?

307
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,380
Surprise me.

308
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,380
Okay.

309
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:24,670
With chicken.

310
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:24,670
You got it.

311
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:27,120
Hey, sweetheart, just take one
of these out to your mom, okay?

312
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,460
Okay, yeah,
um, Dad, this lady

