00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:30,040
wanted hers
with no scallions, so...

314
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:31,380
Oh. Okay. Uh...

315
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:32,420
Whoop! Sorry.

316
00:11:32,420 --> 00:11:34,250
Mr. Chu, uh,
this customer right here,

317
00:11:34,250 --> 00:11:35,920
she wanted this one
without scallions.

318
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:37,380
No special orders.

319
