00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:55,250
Mr. Chu has pivoted
away from the organization.

370
00:13:55,250 --> 00:13:57,250
So we'll get
a new pho guy.

371
00:13:58,540 --> 00:14:01,670
Uh, we tried that,
but, uh, apparently,

372
00:14:01,670 --> 00:14:05,420
