376
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:11,290
Yes.

377
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:16,960
But don't worry,
because...

378
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:19,460
No, no, don't point at him
and say "chili" again.

379
00:14:19,460 --> 00:14:20,670
I wasn't
gonna point at him.

