00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:10,210
Mm-hmm.

493
00:18:10,210 --> 00:18:13,040
And that is why I bought
my <i>own </i>food truck today.

494
00:18:13,040 --> 00:18:14,380
See you in the streets.

